observationText: The hTERT NF1 ipNF95.6 cell line was derived from a plexiform neurofibroma of a patient with neurofibromatosis type 1 and immortalized using the hTERT and Cdk4 transgenes.
The hTERT NF1 ipNF95.6 cell line was cultured in DMEM with 10% FBS and confirmed to be negative for mycoplasma contamination prior to use.
The hTERT NF1 ipNF95.6 cell line was verified by short tandem repeat (STR) DNA profiling.
